rating_comment:
Spacious and clean room located in a nice neighbourhood of the city, not too far from the train station and also quite near from some sites of interests. As described, the bathroom is separate and is ok.
I didn't have the chance to meet Tamzid, but he was reactive when I was sending him messages. The 2 boys that welcomed me were very kind and friendly.
